    <h2>About the ND Catalog</h2>
    <p>The ND catalog contains records for books, journals, maps, DVDs, etc. owned or licensed by the University.  It does not include articles.  The Kresge Law Library has its own <a href="http://law.nd.edu/library-and-technology">catalog</a>.</p>
    <p>For items not owned or licensed by Notre Dame, see <a href="http://eresources.library.nd.edu/databases/worldcat">WorldCat</a>, a catalog of thousands of libraries. You can borrow many items owned by other libraries through <a href="/ill/">Interlibrary Loan</a>.</p>
